## SIR curves (all on same plot)
```{r}
ggplot(
  sir_long,
  aes(
    x = time,
    y = population,
    color = compartment)) +
  geom_line(size = 1) +
  facet_grid(
    baseline_label ~ vaccination_label) +
  labs(
    title = "SIR Model Dynamics Under Different Vaccination Rates",
    x = "Days",
    y = "Population Size",
    color = "Compartment") +
  theme_minimal(base_size = 14)
```

