## summary statistics
```{r}
summary_table <- sir_results %>%
  group_by(
    vaccination,
    baseline_R0) %>%
  summarize(
    peak_infections =
      max(I),
    time_to_peak =
      time[which.max(I)],
    total_infected =
      max(R),
    .groups = "drop")

summary_table
```

